@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = v0
    v0 = (wp.exp(0.30) * (wp.abs(tmp + 0.89) * 0.10))
    v1 = (wp.abs(wp.cos(v0 + 0.18)) / (0.76 / wp.abs(v1 + 0.48)))
    v1 = v0
    data[tid] = v0
